// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3715 — Mass File Rename (blackbasta)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 88deaa47-6918-5e9a-992c-901686911077

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
